# Summary
This documentation page explains how to build an Event Segmentation analysis in Amplitude, detailing the step-by-step process of selecting events, applying properties, choosing measurement types, and segmenting users, as well as customizing the Y-axis with options for dual axes, custom ranges, and unit display formats.

